    &lt;CommentText&gt;I attended the Alexandra Retail Park in Oldham for a camera down my throat. 
From the moment I was greeted by the receptionist to the moment I left the building I felt very safe and cared for. The staff were so kind and caring yet extremely professional and efficient.I was extremely nervous about the procedure but the nurse who carried out the initial checks was very reassuring and the endoscopist and the staff who worked along side her were amazing. 
The appointment ran on time and I was in and out in less than 40 minutes. 
So thank you staff who work at the mobile unit on Alexandra retail park. &lt;/CommentText&gt;
